claim.claim-text:
1. A dual wavelength focal plane comprising: 
a first array of infrared sensing pixel elements; 
a second array of visible light pixel elements adapted to be selective to colors encountered while driving an automobile.

7. A dual wavelength focal plane comprising: 
a first array of infrared sensing pixel elements; 
a second array of sets of three pixel elements adapted to be selective to red, blue and green respectively

8. A sensor for aiding an automobile driver at night, the sensor comprising: 
a first array of infrared sensing pixel elements formed on a silicon substrate; 
a second array of sets of three visible sensors adapted to be selective to red, blue and green respectively, each set of photosensors formed on the silicon substrate beneath the infrared sensing pixel element.
